    "A94, page 21 of 30 In particular, notice that φ2 E and φ2 P should be taken as: -different parameters when the average pulsar-Earth and pulsar-pulsar distance is larger than the coherence length; -the same parameter when the average pulsar-Earth and pulsar-pulsar distance is smaller than the coherence length.",
